<HEADLINE> Jarvis Agent Denies Client Remarks  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- The agent representing St. John's coach Mike
Jarvis has denied that he said his client was considering other
coaching opportunities after ending talks with the Washington
Wizards.
</P>
<P>
   The agent, Rob Ades, denied speaking to an Associated Press
reporter Monday night and saying that Jarvis was considering a
major college coaching position and other NBA possibilities.
</P>
