<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-24 13:12 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> The Top Fives in TV, Movies, Music  </HEADLINE>
By The Associated Press	   
TELEVISION
<TEXT>
<P>
   1. ''ER,'' NBC.
</P>
<P>
   2. ''Frasier,'' NBC.
</P>
<P>
   3. ''Friends,'' NBC.
</P>
<P>
   4. ''Who Wants to Be a Millionaire-Sunday,'' ABC.
</P>
<P>
   5. ''Who Wants to Be a Millionaire-Tuesday,'' ABC.
</P>
<P>
   (From Nielsen Media Research)
FILMS
</P>
<P>
   1. ''Dinosaur,'' Disney.
</P>
<P>
