   June 2: Actor Milo O'Shea is 75. Actress Sally Kellerman is 63.
Actor Stacy Keach (''Titus'') is 59. Musician Charlie Watts of the
Rolling Stones is 59. Actor Jerry Mathers (''Leave It to Beaver'')
is 52. Actress Joanna Gleason is 50. Actor-comedian Dana Carvey is
45. Rapper B-Real with Cypress Hill is 30. Actress Paula Cale
(''Providence'') is 30.
